    "name": "THIEF'S SHELTER",
    "steam_appid": 1430930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THIEF’S SHELTER 是一款 3D Point and Click Psychological Adventure，在这里世界映射出一颗正在崩溃的心智。没有任何事物是稳定的，连你自己的思绪都不可信。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 你即将踏入的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《THIEF'S SHELTER》揭开尘封创伤、扭曲野心，以及操纵一切的非人力量。你的调查与侦探詹姆斯的内心挣扎交织在一起——其中最致命的，是人为诱发的失智症及其后遗症。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将与詹姆斯逐渐崩溃的精神状态对抗，体验幻觉，直面被压抑的记忆。海本庄园会随推进而扭曲变形；搜寻线索，利用专业工具揭开隐藏在眼前的秘密。越是深入，就越难分辨真假——宅邸里真有超自然存在，还是一切都只在你脑中？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/2a39a3858ffc1b34b8d7ffd53d9f08e2.poster.avif?t=1769549047\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/2a39a3858ffc1b34b8d7ffd53d9f08e2.webm?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/2a39a3858ffc1b34b8d7ffd53d9f08e2.mp4?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 一切的开端</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英国伯明翰。</strong> 警队腐败、帮派横行，国家动荡不安。曾经的反犯罪组织“红色教团”如今摇身一变，靠销售健康产品大发其财。然而光鲜外表下，暗藏着骇人的阴谋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搬到伯明翰后，詹姆斯被召去协助调查海本街的一桩离奇凶案。尽管失智发作、恶魔缠身，他仍深陷调查——而这也让他的精神急速恶化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/c3f11b2bf3937424108b7c42db1dd6ca.poster.avif?t=1769549047\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/c3f11b2bf3937424108b7c42db1dd6ca.webm?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/c3f11b2bf3937424108b7c42db1dd6ca.mp4?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 不断变化的案发现场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着调查推进，庄园也在悄然重塑：旧走廊通向未知之地，房门从墙壁“渗”出，整间房间在你眼前滑动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座房子排斥外来者。它轰炸你的感官，展现不应存在之物，并撕开你竭力埋葬的回忆。墙纸像皮肤般剥落，餐桌上闪现悬浮的尸体。是否有人在暗处注视？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并非所有发现都会首次显现——也不一定会在第二次出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次通关看不到全部。VHS 录像带、面具、教团阴谋、詹姆斯的过去……稍不留神便会错过。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/8b42e6aeda9cd2f1b4e6b00d743a42e1.poster.avif?t=1769549047\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/8b42e6aeda9cd2f1b4e6b00d743a42e1.webm?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/8b42e6aeda9cd2f1b4e6b00d743a42e1.mp4?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 日志系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >詹姆斯将新发现写进《回忆录》，关键证据则归档于“侦查笔记”。《回忆录》反映他的精神状态并随之变化；笔记可随时查阅，用来解谜或追踪线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 谜题</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏里的谜题强调观察与推理，而非盲目尝试。想抵达终点，你必须找回与庄园息息相关的四件关键圣物：多阶段机械装置、神秘符号、以及本不该存在的密室正等待破解。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用手电与数码相机，揭示肉眼难辨的真相。UV 光可显现隐形符号、脚印与血迹；相机则让你窥见庄园隐藏的另一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/93d0f60c629b86b30b6deeb6fed409cd.poster.avif?t=1769549047\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/93d0f60c629b86b30b6deeb6fed409cd.webm?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/93d0f60c629b86b30b6deeb6fed409cd.mp4?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 非同寻常的冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许多玩家在初次体验游戏时，会先体验第一层。这意味着你将经历一段完整的旅程——体验“所有”事物——但代价是，有些答案以及某些隐藏内容仍无法触及。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中一个鲜为人知的秘密在于另一个结局，它为那些寻求答案的玩家提供了更深刻的见解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你玩过一次还是一百次，《THIEF'S SHELTER》的目标都是始终有所回报。对于喜欢串联线索、记录笔记并得出新结论的玩家，游戏鼓励社区讨论——在那里，发现和解读会不断共同发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你应该明白，有些东西注定要隐藏起来——也许几个月后、一年后，甚至永远都不会被发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永恒不变的事实是，你永远无法获得所有答案……但你可以比那些只体验过表面的人获得更清晰的理解——而这才是你真正的回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/9ab7e4664b4a1a18929dcf4f8a5a454f.poster.avif?t=1769549047\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/9ab7e4664b4a1a18929dcf4f8a5a454f.webm?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1430930/extras/9ab7e4664b4a1a18929dcf4f8a5a454f.mp4?t=1769549047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 经典题材的现代演绎</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《THIEF'S SHELTER》在《Myst》式点击冒险的基础上焕新升级：电影级演出、顺畅移动与细腻饱满的 3D 场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >导航自然流畅，无需盲目奔走；可选提示与智能路线标记让你始终沉浸于谜团中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• 主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态环境。</strong> 随着剧情推进，庄园不断开辟新区域、重塑旧区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家主导。</strong> 世界自有其运行，不会因你停滞。线索错过便消失，故事因此独一无二，却不会陷入死局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逻辑谜题。</strong> 所有挑战都基于观察与演绎，没有荒诞答案，也无需碰运气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>侦查工具。</strong> UV 光与相机揭示隐秘；证据将影响詹姆斯的心理与剧情走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可重复游玩。</strong> 多次调查可挖掘更深真相：隐藏的 VHS、秘密圣物和全新日志条目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>氛围悬疑。</strong> 经典冒险，现代叙事。没有廉价惊吓，只有层层递进的压迫感、关键抉择与沉浸故事。</p></li></ul>",
